>>The opening sentence of “ >Living with legacy issues” (Politics Watch, Perspective page, Jan. 13, 2016) read: “On December 7, when Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) patriarch Mufti Mohammad Sayeed was laid to rest ...” It should have been January 7.>>“ >The waning lustre of the Budget” (Perspective page, Jan. 13, 2016) referred to the government’s decision to limit the LPG subsidy to those earning Rs.10 lakh or less per annum. It should have been Rs.10 lakh or more per annum.